[SN]TITLE[SN]
In search of the European Dream: Freedom of movement

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
What was the European Dream? What state of health is it in?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
5 May 2016 Last updated at 10:30 BST
In the second of three films, BBC Newsnight's Gabriel Gatehouse focuses on the promise of freedom of movement - and asks how that has stood up in the face of the migrant crisis.
